	<text>
		<body>
			<div type="transcription">
				<!--<p>EHRI-DR-19420323-IT_EN</p>
      <p>Report of the Italian Consul General in Prague, Casto Caruso, to the Ministry of Foreign
        Affairs in Rome and the Italian Embassy in Berlin.</p>
      <p>Cable No. 756/179</p>
      <p>R. Consulate General of <placeName
          ref="#italian-republic">Italy</placeName></p>-->
				<pb facs="EHRI-DR-19420323-IT.jpg" n="1"/>
				<p>Addressed to R. <orgName ref="#g005042">Ministry of Foreign Affairs</orgName>, <placeName ref="#rome">Rome</placeName></p>
				<p>R. Embassy of Italy, <placeName ref="#berlin">Berlin</placeName></p>
				<p>M <persName ref="#p000287">Mussolini</persName></p>
				<p><placeName ref="#prague">Prague</placeName>, <date when="1942-03-23">23th March 1942</date>. XX</p>
				<p>Re: <term ref="#t614" type="subject">Concentration of Jews</term>.</p>
				<p>I have the honour to inform that an important decree concerning the <term ref="#t575" type="subject">transfer</term> of <term
						ref="#t864" type="subject">Jews</term> to a location in the <placeName ref="#l64">Protectorate</placeName> (<placeName
						ref="#l29">Theresienstadt</placeName>) has been published in the Collection of Laws and Decrees of the <ref
						target="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/admindistricts-212">Reichsprotektor</ref>. With this <term ref="#t542"
						type="subject">measure</term> the <term ref="#t872" type="subject">Jewish element</term> will be definitively isolated from
					the remaining <term ref="#t373" type="subject">Aryan</term> population.</p>
				<p>Of course, <placeName ref="#l29">Theresienstadt</placeName> will have to be vacated by <term ref="#t373" type="subject"
						>Aryan</term> citizens. The <ref target="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/admindistricts-212">Reichsprotektor’s</ref>
					decree deals with this <term ref="#t585" type="subject">problem</term> and rules that no <term ref="#t373" type="subject"
						>Aryan</term> person transferred elsewhere shall suffer any <term ref="#t945" type="subject">material</term> loss. All <term
						ref="#t373" type="subject">Aryans</term> living in the area chosen for the <placeName ref="#l64">Protectorate’s</placeName>
					<term ref="#t864" type="subject">Jewish</term>
					<term ref="#t545" type="subject">ghetto</term> will have their losses refunded and will be <term ref="#t1039" type="subject"
						>transferred</term> elsewhere in an appropriate manner. Clearly, despite this measure, those who are to be transferred will
					have to bear some sacrifices for the benefit of all.</p>
				<p>The local <term ref="#t341" type="subject">press</term> emphasizes that these sacrifices will in any case be largely offset by the
					huge advantages that cleansing the <placeName ref="#l64">Protectorate</placeName> of <term ref="#t864" type="subject">Jews</term>
					will provide to the entire <placeName ref="#czechoslovakia">Czech</placeName>
					<term ref="#t373" type="subject">Aryan</term> population.</p>
				<p>I enclose a full translation of the <ref target="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/admindistricts-212"
						>Reichsprotektor’s</ref> decree.</p>
				<p><persName ref="#ehri_dr_caruso_casto">Caruso</persName></p>
